96
00:04:01,321 --> 00:04:04,280
Well... Guess what? Me too.

97
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,297
Come with me?

98
00:04:10,460 --> 00:04:15,357
As a soldier... I like to get straight to the point...

99
00:04:15,610 --> 00:04:18,169
There's something I wanted to say...

100
00:04:18,169 --> 00:04:21,420
I'm sure you know what it's about.

101
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:26,015
