169
00:08:16,180 --> 00:08:18,444
It's sorted out.

170
00:08:18,444 --> 00:08:19,909
How?

171
00:08:20,220 --> 00:08:22,282
Just... Sorted out.

172
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:28,540
Bless yer... Yer luk nice... Young, if Oi may say so...

173
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:34,090
'Young' is stretchin' it...

174
00:08:34,090 --> 00:08:37,825
The grub dees days... It takes a toll on yer...

175
00:08:37,825 --> 00:08:40,430
Aye, roi...

176
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:46,690
All our lives, we've done everythin' ter take care av Mamai, Da, brothers, an' each other...

177
00:08:46,690 --> 00:08:51,432
Dad used ter walk two miles every mornin'.

178
00:08:51,432 --> 00:08:54,683
All 'is life.

179
00:08:54,683 --> 00:08:57,000
But me...

180
00:08:57,000 --> 00:09:01,320
My joints craic an' pop an' 'urt al' de time.

181
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:05,461
Have sum marmalade. It'll ease de pain.

182
00:09:05,461 --> 00:09:07,179
Really?

183
00:09:07,179 --> 00:09:09,674
Always worked for us.

184
00:09:09,674 --> 00:09:15,410
We make lashings av marmalade! An' 'av it loike afters!

185
00:09:15,410 --> 00:09:18,648
I'll ask Vishal ter git sum...

186
00:09:18,648 --> 00:09:22,929
Not sure if we can git sum good marmalade the-day though...

187
00:09:22,929 --> 00:09:26,420
Did Vishal git into university?

188
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:28,285
Aye.

189
00:09:28,515 --> 00:09:31,840
We're waitin' for 'is result...

190
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,921
But oi'm confident 'e'll ace it.

191
00:09:33,921 --> 00:09:36,440
Vishal...

192
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:39,130
Is jist loike Vijay...

193
