Vijay never failed an exam. Ever.

194
00:09:43,460 --> 00:09:46,002
Just loike Sherali.

195
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:49,865
He did everythin' on 'is own...

196
00:09:49,865 --> 00:09:55,331
We barely knew aboyt 'is exams an' al'...

197
00:09:56,331 --> 00:10:01,286
He'd tell us... Whaen 'e'd git 'is result...

198
