But Vijay wus never a 'assle...

201
00:10:12,001 --> 00:10:14,140
Sherali...

202
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:16,961
Always listened ter me...

203
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:22,511
Ever since 'e lef us... We've been... Uneasy... Troubled...

204
00:10:22,511 --> 00:10:24,414
Aye...

205
00:10:25,553 --> 00:10:30,553
Our kids are who we live for...
-Absolutely...

206
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:35,748
'E's de only wan oi 'ad...

207
00:10:35,748 --> 00:10:38,867
My son-in-law is so greedy... So greedy...

208
00:10:38,867 --> 00:10:41,040
God forgive 'im...

209
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:47,160
I canny even tell yer waaat a 'assle 'e's been after Vijay's death!

210
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:48,860
Gud Lord...

211
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:51,020
I can understan'...

212
00:10:51,426 --> 00:10:59,350
We've done everythin' for our kids al' our lives... But we've got nathin'... Naw wan...

213
00:10:59,350 --> 00:11:03,575
An' ter tink... We wouldn't be cryin' loike dis...

214
00:11:03,575 --> 00:11:05,822
For our lost sons...

215
00:11:05,822 --> 00:11:09,700
If our nashuns did not fight dees bleedin wars al' de bleedin time!

216
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:14,197
War killed dem... An' us...

217
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:20,999
Aye...

218
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:29,857
Why'd you have to talk about any of this?

219
00:11:29,857 --> 00:11:33,953
Couldn't you talk about something good?

220
00:11:37,090 --> 00:11:39,296
