221
00:11:40,827 --> 00:11:43,545
You're making her cry too...

222
00:11:46,230 --> 00:11:48,466
Mrs Malhotra...

223
00:11:49,201 --> 00:11:51,580
Please...

224
00:11:51,580 --> 00:11:58,229
Talk all you want about Kathiya Wala Bazaar... Or the woods of Amritsar...

225
00:11:58,229 --> 00:12:02,490
Or the river Jhelum...

226
00:12:02,490 --> 00:12:06,220
But...

227
00:12:06,220 --> 00:12:10,540
Let's not talk...

228
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:15,050
