Hey.

232
00:12:31,944 --> 00:12:33,188
Hey.

233
00:12:33,188 --> 00:12:36,818
You stopped coming here in the morning because of me!

234
00:12:36,818 --> 00:12:41,504
No... I just ain't that regular... I come here when I feel like...

235
00:12:41,504 --> 00:12:47,082
It's quite reassuring, you know... That it's not because of me...

236
00:12:49,530 --> 00:12:51,162
Anyway...

237
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:54,723
This is for you.

238
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:58,494
