243
00:13:37,300 --> 00:13:38,902
Ma'am...
-Hmm?

244
00:13:38,902 --> 00:13:41,656
Got this letter.
-Who sent it?

245
00:13:41,656 --> 00:13:43,652
No idea.

246
00:13:44,950 --> 00:13:46,789
Thank you.

247
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:18,142
